<section class="section section-manifesto">
  <div class="manifesto-grid">
    <div class="manifesto-headline">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">THE PROMISE</div>
      <h2 class="section-h2">Your tokens never leave your machine. Neither do you.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="manifesto-list">
      <div class="manifesto-item">
        <div class="manifesto-k">No API keys</div>
        <div class="manifesto-v">tokenuse never authenticates with any provider. It only reads files you already have.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="manifesto-item">
        <div class="manifesto-k">No proxy</div>
        <div class="manifesto-v">No traffic flows through tokenuse. Your editor talks to your model exactly the way it always has.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="manifesto-item">
        <div class="manifesto-k">No telemetry</div>
        <div class="manifesto-v">There is no analytics endpoint. The default build has zero network dependency.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="manifesto-item">
        <div class="manifesto-k">Two opt-in network paths</div>
        <div class="manifesto-v">Currency rates and the LiteLLM pricing snapshot, gated behind feature flags. You choose when to pull them.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
